Editor’s note, April 2: There have been significant developments in the coronavirus pandemic since this story was last updated.
And it’s possible that as we discover more of these cases, Covid-19 will look less deadly.
A dramatic — and unprecedented — response played out in China, the country with the most Covid-19 cases.
Some governments have so far been able to halt the spread of coronavirus within their borders, seemingly through quick action.
Perhaps public health measures — identifying cases fast, putting infected people in isolation — will slow the spread of this coronavirus.